Consent to Personal Data Collection and Use
By submitting this form, you consent to the collection, processing, and use of your personal data within the framework of this research study. Your data will be used exclusively for research purposes and the improvement of medical practices.
Data Storage and Hosting
We inform you that your personal data will be stored on cloud servers provided by [CLOUD SERVICE PROVIDER NAME]. [PROVIDER NAME] implements technical and organizational security measures in compliance with international standards to protect your data.
Important Notice: Your data may be transferred and stored outside your country of residence, including locations where data protection laws may differ from those in your jurisdiction. Such transfers are conducted within the framework of appropriate protection mechanisms recognized by applicable data protection regulations.
Data Protection Commitment
We are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy:

Your data will be processed confidentially and securely
Processing complies with applicable data protection regulations (including GDPR for EU residents, HIPAA for US health data where applicable)
Data will be retained only for the period necessary to fulfill the research purposes, and in any case for a maximum duration of [X] years from the end of the study
Access to your data is restricted to authorized research personnel only

Your Rights
Under applicable data protection laws, you have the following rights:

Access: Request a copy of your personal data
Rectification: Correct inaccurate or incomplete data
Erasure: Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")
Restriction: Limit how your data is processed
Data Portability: Receive your data in a structured, commonly used, machine-readable format
Objection: Object to data processing for legitimate reasons
Withdrawal of Consent: Withdraw your consent at any time

Exercising Your Rights
To exercise these rights or for any questions regarding your data management, please contact:
Data Protection Contact: [STUDY EMAIL ADDRESS]
Principal Investigator: [PI NAME AND INSTITUTION]
You also have the right to file a complaint with your local data protection supervisory authority.
Voluntary Participation
Your participation in this study is entirely voluntary. You may withdraw your consent at any time without providing justification and without affecting:

The lawfulness of processing based on consent before withdrawal
Your medical care or relationship with your healthcare provider

To withdraw consent, simply contact the email address provided above.
Legal Basis and Purpose
Legal Basis for Processing: Consent of the data subject (Article 6.1.a of GDPR where applicable)
Purpose of Processing: Medical research to advance knowledge and improve patient outcomes in [SPECIFIC MEDICAL FIELD]
Additional Safeguards

All data is anonymized/pseudonymized before analysis
